{"id": 57651, "date": "2025-07-09T04:00:28", "date_gmt": "2025-07-09T11:00:28", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57651"}, "modified": "2026-03-02T15:18:18", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-02T23:18:18", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-9-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/09/kingdom-of-days-july-9-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 9"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band headline at The Main Point in Bryn Mawr, Pennsylvania. Bruce is no stranger to having his name misspelled by now, but this is a new one.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11193\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/mainpoint-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mainpoint-1.jpg?fit=499%2C293&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"499,293\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"mainpoint\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mainpoint-1.jpg?fit=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mainpoint-1.jpg?fit=499%2C293&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11193 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mainpoint-1.jpg?resize=499%2C293&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mainpoint-1.jpg?w=499&amp;ssl=1 499w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mainpoint-1.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce sits down for an interview with WNEW-FM DJ Dave Herman in San Diego. (The interview will air in September on the King Biscuit Flower Hour.)\u00a0 As with Mary Turner a few days earlier, Bruce is loose, talkative, and funny. This interview is definitely worth a listen.</p>\n<div id=\"v-1tvtbjLH-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/1tvtbjLH?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p>That evening, Bruce plays a gig at the San Diego Sports Arena, where he sings &#8220;Not Fade Away&#8221; and &#8220;Gloria&#8221; as lead-ins to &#8220;She&#8217;s the One&#8221; for the first time.</p>\n<div id=\"v-9D8CJQei-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/9D8CJQei?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28208\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-07-09-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-09.jpg?fit=448%2C963&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"448,963\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593086107&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-07-09\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-09.jpg?fit=140%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-09.jpg?fit=448%2C963&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28208 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-09.jpg?resize=448%2C963&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"448\" height=\"963\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-09.jpg?w=448&amp;ssl=1 448w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-09.jpg?resize=140%2C300&amp;ssl=1 140w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1981:</strong>\u00a0Bruce and the E Street Band close out their opening stand at the Brendan Byrne Arena in the Meadowlands, and Gary U.S. Bonds joins them on stage for &#8220;Jole Blon&#8221; and &#8220;This Little Girl.&#8221; Bruce&#8217;s performance of &#8220;Jersey Girl&#8221; will be released in 1984 as the B-side to &#8220;Cover Me&#8221; as well as on the <em>Live 1975-85\u00a0</em>box set. This concert is available for purchase as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/c6InmR1IPs4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LRWZ11xRVwA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/78pdEP9Pr4s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WCcS5hVcVgs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28210\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-07-09-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-09.jpg?fit=887%2C959&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"887,959\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593086396&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-07-09\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-09.jpg?fit=277%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-09.jpg?fit=758%2C820&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28210 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-09.jpg?resize=758%2C820&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-09.jpg?w=887&amp;ssl=1 887w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-09.jpg?resize=277%2C300&amp;ssl=1 277w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-09.jpg?resize=768%2C830&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>At Night Two in Richfield, Ohio on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour, Bruce plays &#8220;No Surrender&#8221; acoustically for the first time ever, along with the tour premiere of &#8220;Darkness on the Edge of Town.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-Eurx5bco-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Eurx5bco?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/i2uzyHlLjSs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zBpMD6Z-NROlIhXjAwaWOdZ\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>Bruce brings the Tunnel of Love Tour to Sheffield for the first of two nights. &#8220;Spare Parts&#8221; from this show will be released on the <em>Spare Parts</em> EP and on\u00a0<em>Video Anthology</em>. Bruce spends time with Roy Orbison at the hotel before the show.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HKH3C3b2HzU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jAgD8cwvcxk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"52334\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/manchester_evening_news_1988_07_11_6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?fit=1268%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1268,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?fit=149%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?fit=507%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-52334 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C1530&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1530\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?w=1268&amp;ssl=1 1268w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?resize=149%2C300&amp;ssl=1 149w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?resize=507%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 507w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1550&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?resize=761%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 761w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Manchester_Evening_News_1988_07_11_6-scaled.jpg?resize=1015%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1015w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1989:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Cats on a Smooth Surface at The Stone Pony for &#8220;Travelin&#8217; Band.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IcBM6UlaIzA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new touring band play their second of five nights at Wembley Arena in London.</p>\n<div id=\"v-mY6CjOdb-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/mY6CjOdb?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1995:\u00a0</strong>One of the stranger collaborations of Bruce&#8217;s career: Bruce travels to Berlin, where he plays a short concert at Cafe Eckstein with Wolfgang Niedecken and His Leopardefellband. The purpose of the show is to yield a new recording and video for &#8220;Hungry Heart,&#8221; which will be released on video and on the <em>Hungry Heart</em> EP (sort of&#8211;it will actually feature Bruce&#8217;s new vocals over the original instrumental track, and it&#8217;s kind of jarring. Compare the official video with the raw footage below). The setlist also features several covers, including Dylan&#8217;s &#8220;Knockin&#8217; on Heaven&#8217;s Door&#8221; and &#8220;Highway 61 Revisited.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0My2AqPFpFg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Bwj6KB8sfO0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SGLVwl9JFEg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLmxwNSnqgfefUrF8aoCMV1UO6oh6FA8TM\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce guest-stars at Joe Grushecky&#8217;s acoustic show at Hooligans in Long Branch, New Jersey on three songs: &#8220;Never Be Enough Time,&#8221; &#8220;Pumping Iron,&#8221; and &#8220;Brown Eyed Girl.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3007\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-0709/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1999-0709.jpg?fit=250%2C240&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"250,240\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-0709\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1999-0709.jpg?fit=250%2C240&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1999-0709.jpg?fit=250%2C240&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3007 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1999-0709.jpg?resize=250%2C240&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19462\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-07-09/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-09.jpg?fit=383%2C959&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"383,959\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593091290&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-07-09\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-